reviewText: Grandchildren enjoy these tapes.  Shipped quickly.  Great price.
My grandchildren didn't like it as well as the last one they had. Not as interesting. It did not hold my interest either.

Danger Rangers are a great teaching tool for children. I sit with my grandchildren and we watch it together. We talk about what they have learned thru the great safety points that the DVDs teach. They love Danger Rangers!
